{
  "stem": "23350.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Our-- being in Birkenau was only because as long-- if they will-- might need us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because we-- it was 1944, and in August, and we didn't have-- they didn't get any numbers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was only a question whether we will be gassed or whether they will need us for work, because they still needed people for work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the question was now-- so we were standing on [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every morning, 6:00 in the morning till 12:00, we were being counted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were standing in fives and being counted, like sheep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had one to count us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was Irma Grese.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was a real sadist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was very beautiful, but ice cold beautiful, if you know what I mean.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Blond and blue eyes, but ice cold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was always walking around with dogs, and-- big dogs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she always had like a [INAUDIBLE], you know, to-- to hit you with-- to hit you with.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "God forbid if somebody didn't stand straight, or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- well, anyway, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and I would have been selected with my sister, because we were in fives.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They told us to stand in fives, outside the barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because between the barracks, there was enough-- was exactly the same-- let's say, there is a barrack, and there is a space exactly as wide as the barrack.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then again, a barrack and exactly the same width of a barrack.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was for us to stand to be counted on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as we were-- were called out to stand in fives, I went through with my sister.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I thought, now I'll be out of Birkenau, of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
